title: Train Simple Adobe CC Color Grading Tips
description:
Adobe CC Color Grading Tips

In Adobe CC Color Grading Tips, Chad Troftgruben takes you
through color grading workflows in Premiere Pro CC and After
Effects CC. Then, you will also learn about the new Color
Themes and Looks features in the Adobe Capture CC mobile app
which can assist you in your color grading. You'll also learn
about some special effects to polish up your color graded
footage
